    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fiction which contains elements of autobiography, or fictionalized autobiography. The term was originally coined by author Serge Dubrovsky in 1977.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
